title: Episode 210: Put It In Your Nose (Feat. Dovey Magnum)
itunes:title: Episode 210: Put It In Your Nose (Feat. Dovey Magnum)
description:
Reggae artist Dovey Magnum joins the ladies of Lip Service this week. The ladies cover a range of topics including when the balls to penis ratio isn't right, having to fart during sex, pre-sex rituals and much more. Dovey goes 0 to 100 real quick when expressing her passion for 'putting it in your nose,' while Gigi opens up and gets candid about her recent breakup. Enjoy!
